      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>For more details on authoring materials in USD with LOPs, such as adding material references and variants, see <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.sidefx.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LOPS tutorial 1</a>. We will outline the basic material workflow with <em>RenderMan</em> materials.</p><h3 id=\"CreatingaMaterialinSolaris-CreateMaterial\">Create Material</h3><p>Materials are created within the Material Library LOP.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080427&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=387\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080427&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"551\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640772\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640743\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cc09336c-dc6a-40dd-9071-0dda968e3f53\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080427&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1697&amp;height=731 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080427&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=387 1x\"></span><p /><p>Dive inside the <em>materiallibrary </em>and once inside, create a RenderMan Material Builder(Hydra) node. </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080427&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080427&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640769\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640743\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f2d406d7-d2b6-427a-acbb-6fb12fcd3956\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/>Inside your new RenderMan material builder node, this is where you can create your wonderful shading networks.<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080427&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080427&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640766\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640743\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5d832285-44fc-4b48-a8ce-c8e4ec78e4a1\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p /><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Go back up to the Material Library parameters and auto-fill materials. This will add your new material to the Solaris Scene Graph, ready to be assigned</span></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=541\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"770\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640763\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_4.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640743\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4791b5f2-e482-44a3-bbbb-081c9aaf1fd6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1698&amp;height=1021 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=541 1x\"></span><hr/><h3 id=\"CreatingaMaterialinSolaris-AssignMaterials\">Assign Materials</h3><p>Fill in the Primitives and Material Path parameters on the <em>assignmaterial  </em>node for each material assignment. You can either type the paths or drag and drop from the Scene Graph Tree.  You can also use the <em>materiallinker </em>node<br/><br/>Here we are assigning the material we created above to /ToyBox_PlateB/PlateGeo</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=721\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1027\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640760\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_5.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640743\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ede4f443-b76b-4d9e-98a8-b155313e1811\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1698&amp;height=1362 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080187&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=721 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080186&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=721\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080186&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1027\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640757\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_6.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640743\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"66c17249-28ac-4239-b0a0-b80b584fb650\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080186&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1698&amp;height=1362 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/RenderMan_Solaris_CreateMaterial_6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080186&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=900&amp;height=721 1x\"></span><hr/><h2 id=\"CreatingaMaterialinSolaris-Multi-RendererWorkflow\">Multi-Renderer Workflow</h2><ul><li><p>Solaris supports multi-render materials. To create, wire the different renderers' material networks to a collect node. The correct network is selected when a hydra render is started. <br/><br/></p></li></ul><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"9360819c-0594-4207-a282-523db83d193f\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>PxrMaterialBuilder is not yet supported in Solaris, which is the default RfH workflow you see elsewhere. To package a RenderMan material network, create a subnetwork VOP.</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/rfh_solaris_multirender.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080613&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=612&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/rfh_solaris_multirender.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080613&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"612\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640781\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_solaris_multirender.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640743\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3952f798-b03e-4044-b991-cd982e4ba38a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/rfh_solaris_multirender.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080613&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=612&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/rfh_solaris_multirender.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080613&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=612&amp;height=384 1x\"></span><p /><ul><li><p>The Subnetwork VOP contains a subinput and a suboutput. Wire bxdf and displacement connections to the suboutput. These outputs should then be connected to the material library's collect node. The subinput VOP can be used for indirect inputs from the material library network. </p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/rfh_solaris_subnet.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080613&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=609&amp;height=352\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544640743/rfh_solaris_subnet.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080613&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"352\" data-width=\"609\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544640778\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfh_solaris_subnet.PNG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544640743\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5f8df313-9f0d-453a-9d6d-21ce43dd5e9f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/rfh_solaris_subnet.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080613&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=609&amp;height=352 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544640743/rfh_solaris_subnet.PNG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433080613&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=609&amp;height=352 1x\"></span><p />"
    }
